==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Stargazing
<hw>Star"gaz`ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act or
practice of observing the stars with attention; contemplation of the
stars as connected with astrology or astronomy.</def>
<rj><au>Swift.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Hence, absent-mindedness; abstraction.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Staringly</ent>⟦br⟧
